GET /user/logout
Log out the user

POST /user/auth
Log in the user using persona

GET /presentation/:user/:title
Return the presentation as an html file.

POST /presentation/:user/:title/:slide
{
	content : <section><p>Content of the slide</p></section>
}
Save the content of the slide

GET /list/presentations
Return a list of the presentations title alongside with the first slide.

GET /list/templates
Return a list of all available templates

GET /template/:name
Return the template as an html file.

POST /new/presentation 
{	
	title : titre de la presentation,
	template : http://url.of.the/template.html
}
Create a new presentation
